OL,5, The government has said it has to      
OL,6, "prepare for the worst" as the UK's    
OL,7, energy firms continue to come under    
OL,8, pressure from soaring gas prices.      
OL,10,FSmall business minister Paul Scully    
OL,11,Ftold the BBC his department was working
OL,12,Fclosely with regulator Ofgem to protect
OL,13,Fcustomers if more firms went bust.     
OL,15,FNearly 1.5 million customers have been 
OL,16,Fhit in just two weeks by energy firms  
OL,17,Fcollapsing under soaring gas prices.   
OL,19,FAmong them are Avro Energy and Green,  
OL,20,Fwhich ceased trading on Wednesday.     
